{
"template_meta": {
"template_name": "sun_kissed_lifestyle_portrait_right_facing",
"usage": "shopify/ecommerce product page - Lifestyle / Benefit Shot",
"version": "2.0"
},
"technical_specs": {
"resolution_width": 2000,
"resolution_height": 2000,
"aspect_ratio": "1:1",
"base_canvas_color": "RGB(255,255,255)",
"file_format": "JPG/PNG"
},
"prompt": "Close-up lifestyle portrait shot at low angle. Subject: young Black woman with braided hair and radiant, glowing skin. Clothing: gray sports bra — only the straps visible in frame. Pose: facing 45° to the right (away from camera), head tilted slightly back, eyes closed, broad peaceful smile of pure bliss and wellbeing.\n\nAction: She holds [PRODUCT_NAME] by [BRAND_NAME] with a delicate fingertip grip — fingers on the sides/edges of the product — bringing it close to her cheek and jawline. The product is clearly visible and sharp in frame.\n\nEnvironment: outdoor nature scene. Background: soft bokeh trees, lush green foliage, blue sky with clouds. Lighting: natural golden hour daylight — warm, sun-kissed glow, soft directional shadows from above-left.\n\nPRODUCT INTEGRATION (CRITICAL): The product lighting MUST match the golden hour environment — warm highlights on the sun-facing side, soft shadow on the opposite side, subtle ambient bounce from the sky. The product must look as though it was photographed in this scene, not composited. Zero hard cutout edges. Zero flat or studio lighting on the product.\n\nTypography: [HEADLINE] top-left corner, large bold editorial serif, color [TEXT_COLOR]. Product benefit subheadline directly below in [ACCENT_COLOR], medium weight."
}

