            "id": "btn_nope",
            "type": "circle_button",
            "icon": "{user_inputs.action_buttons[1].icon}",
            "icon_color": "{user_inputs.action_buttons[1].color_hex}",
            "background": "#FFFFFF",
            "diameter": "70px",
            "shadow": "0 3px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.12)"
          },
          {
            "id": "btn_super_like",
            "type": "circle_button",
            "icon": "{user_inputs.action_buttons[2].icon}",
            "icon_color": "{user_inputs.action_buttons[2].color_hex}",
            "background": "#FFFFFF",
            "diameter": "70px",
            "shadow": "0 3px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.12)"
          },
          {
            "id": "btn_like",
            "type": "circle_button",
            "icon": "{user_inputs.action_buttons[3].icon}",
            "icon_color": "{user_inputs.action_buttons[3].color_hex}",
            "background": "#FFFFFF",
            "diameter": "70px",
            "shadow": "0 3px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.12)"
          },
          {
            "id": "btn_boost",
            "type": "circle_button",
            "icon": "{user_inputs.action_buttons[4].icon}",
            "icon_color": "{user_inputs.action_buttons[4].color_hex}",
            "background": "#FFFFFF",
            "diameter": "70px",
            "shadow": "0 3px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.12)"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
  "generative_image_prompt": "A 2000x2000px square social media ad for {user_inputs.app_name}, styled as a dating app profile screen. White header bar at the top (9% of canvas height) with the {user_inputs.app_name} logo centred \u2014 extract the wordmark onto white, stripping any dark background, preserving brand colours. Thin #E8E8E8 bottom border on the header. Below, a large rounded-corner card (border-radius 40px, subtle drop shadow) fills most of the canvas with a smooth linear gradient from {user_inputs.card_gradient_top_hex} at the top to {user_inputs.card_gradient_bottom_hex} at the bottom. The product ({user_inputs.product_image}) is placed on the right side of the card at approximately x=68%, with its top and cap extending CLEARLY above the card boundary into the white header zone by at least 15-20% of its height. Render the product photorealistically with soft studio lighting, a specular highlight on the cap, and a soft drop shadow at the base coloured as a dark tint of the gradient. On the lower-left of the card: extrabold white sans-serif text '{user_inputs.brand_name} {user_inputs.product_name}' at approximately 70px weight 800, line-height 1.05, with a small inline frosted pill badge '{user_inputs.product_variant}' immediately to the right on the same baseline. Below the name: an icon-text row with a pronoun circle icon and '{user_inputs.pronoun_label}' in small white text. Below that: a magnifying glass icon and '{user_inputs.bio_text}' in smaller white text (approximately 27-30% of headline size). At the bottom of the image on the grey canvas: 5 white circular buttons centred in a row with even spacing \u2014 amber rewind, coral-red X, blue star, teal heart, purple lightning bolt. All buttons have a soft drop shadow. The overall aesthetic precisely mimics a Tinder/Bumble profile swipe screen. Output: 2000x2000px, 1:1, RGB."
}
